\n2. ViewModel OBSERVES the `btn_clicked`ACTION
\n3. ViewModel INSTANTLY UPDATES `btn_color` STATE
\n4. View OBSERVES the `btn_color` UPDATE
\n5. View changes button color"
                android:textAppearance="@style/TextAppearance.AppCompat.Body2" />

            <Button
                android:id="@+id/changeStateInstantlyButton"
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:layout_margin="16dp"
                android:text="Change state instantly" />

        </LinearLayout>

        <LinearLayout
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:layout_margin="16dp"
            android:background="#22FF00FF"
            android:orientation="vertical">

            <TextView
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:layout_gravity="center"
                android:layout_marginStart="16dp"
                android:layout_marginTop="16dp"
                android:layout_marginEnd="16dp"
                android:text="1. View ACTIVATES an `btn_clicked` ACTION
\n2. ViewModel OBSERVES the `btn_clicked`ACTION
\n3. ViewModel ASYNC UPDATES `btn_color` STATE
\n4. View OBSERVES the `btn_color` UPDATE
\n5. View changes button color"
                android:textAppearance="@style/TextAppearance.AppCompat.Body2" />

            <Button
